stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> PENDING : A sends
  PENDING --> ACCEPTED : B sends back (mutual)
  PENDING --> REJECTED : B rejects
  PENDING --> CANCELLED : A cancels
  ACCEPTED --> DISCONNECTED : Either disconnects
  ACCEPTED --> BLOCKED : Either blocks
  DISCONNECTED --> [*]
  REJECTED --> [*]
  CANCELLED --> [*]
  BLOCKED --> [*]